    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个全面控制和无尽战争的世界中，你是约翰·霍尔登，一个被困在战火纷飞的阴暗城镇中的逃兵。利用一切可用的手段生存下来并逃离这座被诅咒的城市：闯入房屋，偷取食物和药品，磨练你的偷盗技巧，并影响城镇居民的命运。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3248910/extras/4bf768737155468145227e35eafaf847.webp?t=1771416863\" width=616 height=32 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3248910/extras/1f6f466a8f02b8b379f8cbc60b7acf4d.poster.avif?t=1771416863\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3248910/extras/1f6f466a8f02b8b379f8cbc60b7acf4d.webm?t=1771416863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3248910/extras/1f6f466a8f02b8b379f8cbc60b7acf4d.mp4?t=1771416863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将拥有丰富的工具和装备：包括撬锁器、撬棍、抓钩和炸药等。此外，还可以利用周围环境：寻找或创造备选路线，潜伏于暗影，不露声色，或者制造噪音，分散他人注意力。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3248910/extras/5c42ddb548b9a6cc1168a0bd65cf3e21.webp?t=1771416863\" width=616 height=32 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3248910/extras/5c33fb8381f72637df133f6a2c84c544.poster.avif?t=1771416863\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3248910/extras/5c33fb8381f72637df133f6a2c84c544.webm?t=1771416863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3248910/extras/5c33fb8381f72637df133f6a2c84c544.mp4?t=1771416863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到这座城市。在这里，你的每一步都被党派监控着，而在幕后，意识形态相互冲突，权力斗争永不停息。无情的官僚们占据了政府的殿堂。街头，劫掠者和走私贩子经营着他们的生意。在所有紧闭的大门背后，人们梦想着自由，而瘟疫在贫民窟肆虐。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3248910/extras/484fbdf1f0506b76b03eb979df259282.webp?t=1771416863\" width=616 height=32 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3248910/extras/fb74480b5db76594ed9c8c771e32b0a1.poster.avif?t=1771416863\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3248910/extras/fb74480b5db76594ed9c8c771e32b0a1.webm?t=1771416863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3248910/extras/fb74480b5db76594ed9c8c771e32b0a1.mp4?t=1771416863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过复杂的RPG系统打造你自己的玩法风格，体验近100种不同的技能和天赋。在8个不同的精通路径中发展你的角色，成为一名诡秘莫测的扒手、熟练的黑客或魅力十足的骗子。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3248910/extras/da4ae759d036e389b6e09f7dcefa6dd4.webp?t=1771416863\" width=616 height=32 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸式模拟的潜行RPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >充满秘密和冒险的半开放世界</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完全自由规划盗窃活动</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深度模拟市民的行为</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以非致命方式处理敌人</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >非线性故事，多种结局</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >融入讽刺和黑色幽默的黑暗反乌托邦</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于《离经叛盗》拓展的世界观</p></li></ul>",
